summary: Squirtle Saxophone - Celebrating the success of the vital TikTok meme - Squirtle Saxophone. An intriguing blend of both nostalgia and modern internet culture. It features Squirtle, masterfully playing the saxophone solo which is also synonymous with the iconic Epic Sax Guy meme. The catchy yet delightfully absurd fusion has captivated audiences creating one of the most culturally significant musical moments on the internet. - We introduce to you, Squirtle Saxophone!
